  <section>
    <h2>Accessibility</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Pure CSS:</strong> No JavaScript required for basic functionality</li>
      <li><strong>Semantic HTML:</strong> Uses native checkbox and label elements</li>
      <li><strong>Keyboard Navigation:</strong> Tab key works naturally with labels and focusable content</li>
      <li><strong>Screen Reader Support:</strong> Proper labeling with SheetTitle and SheetDescription</li>
      <li><strong>Click Outside to Close:</strong> Clicking the overlay closes the sheet</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

